    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39644.0,
      "end_time": 42908.0,
      "text": "my comparison it has to be\nto a similar gas powered car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 42908.0,
      "end_time": 44493.0,
      "text": "I've seen a lot of comments there"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 44493.0,
      "end_time": 46425.0,
      "text": "well my Honda this, or my KIA that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 46425.0,
      "end_time": 49348.0,
      "text": "yes of course, those are\ncheap economical cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 49348.0,
      "end_time": 52996.0,
      "text": "they do not compare to these\nluxury high end sedans."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 52996.0,
      "end_time": 55641.0,
      "text": "So for this analysis I'm going to use"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 55641.0,
      "end_time": 58641.0,
      "text": "a Mercedes Benz S-Class, an Audi A7,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 59588.0,
      "end_time": 62687.0,
      "text": "and a BMW 7 Series, and I'm gonna look"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 62687.0,
      "end_time": 65545.0,
      "text": "at the cost of ownership,\nthe actually maintenance cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 65545.0,
      "end_time": 69535.0,
      "text": "of those cars compared to\nwhat I pay for my Tesla."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 69535.0,
      "end_time": 72265.0,
      "text": "So first I should mention\nthat Tesla has had"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 72265.0,
      "end_time": 74527.0,
      "text": "some reliability issues,\nin fact just recently"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 74527.0,
      "end_time": 77151.0,
      "text": "Reuters reported that they're spending"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 77151.0,
      "end_time": 80607.0,
      "text": "about 1,000 dollars per\nvehicle on warranty repairs"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 80607.0,
      "end_time": 82825.0,
      "text": "compared to Ford and GM which are spending"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 82825.0,
      "end_time": 85919.0,
      "text": "about 400 to 700 dollars per vehicle."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 85919.0,
      "end_time": 88799.0,
      "text": "So Tesla's actually having\nto repair these a lot more"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 88799.0,
      "end_time": 90527.0,
      "text": "and spending a lot more money."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 90527.0,
      "end_time": 92575.0,
      "text": "All I care about though\nis how much it actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 92575.0,
      "end_time": 94964.0,
      "text": "is gonna cost me and kind\nof what the experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 94964.0,
      "end_time": 96415.0,
      "text": "is gonna be like."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 96415.0,
      "end_time": 97908.0,
      "text": "So let's take a look at the data now"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 97908.0,
      "end_time": 100319.0,
      "text": "and see what it actually tells us."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 100319.0,
      "end_time": 103263.0,
      "text": "First off Tesla offers\na prepaid service plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 103263.0,
      "end_time": 105695.0,
      "text": "which spans three, four, and eight years"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 105695.0,
      "end_time": 107615.0,
      "text": "depending on which one you choose."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 107615.0,
      "end_time": 109684.0,
      "text": "This will reduce your overall cost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 109684.0,
      "end_time": 112137.0,
      "text": "but we'll compare those\nalongside not having"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 112137.0,
      "end_time": 114377.0,
      "text": "any prepaid plan as well, so I'll have"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 114377.0,
      "end_time": 116233.0,
      "text": "all three examples here."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 116233.0,
      "end_time": 118452.0,
      "text": "So looking at the total\nmaintenance cost here"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 118452.0,
      "end_time": 121567.0,
      "text": "over five years you can see\nthat all three Tesla options"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 121567.0,
      "end_time": 125471.0,
      "text": "are a lot cheaper than\nall the other options,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 125471.0,
      "end_time": 127796.0,
      "text": "the Mercedes, the BMW, and the Audi even"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 127796.0,
      "end_time": 130996.0,
      "text": "are just many times over more expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 130996.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133599.0,
      "text": "than owning a Tesla in\nterms of maintenance."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 133599.0,
      "end_time": 135753.0,
      "text": "So if you take a look at\nthe total maintenance cost"
