    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 140404.0,
      "end_time": 143796.0,
      "text": "clocking in at around 18,000\ndollars in maintenance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 143796.0,
      "end_time": 146953.0,
      "text": "the BMW 7 Series clocking\nin around 17,000 dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 146953.0,
      "end_time": 149748.0,
      "text": "just behind it, the Audi\nis significantly cheaper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 149748.0,
      "end_time": 151881.0,
      "text": "around 10,000 dollars, or 9,500,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 151881.0,
      "end_time": 153972.0,
      "text": "and then all of the Tesla options"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 153972.0,
      "end_time": 156127.0,
      "text": "are just significantly\ncheaper than all of those."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 156127.0,
      "end_time": 159284.0,
      "text": "In fact, the most expensive\none is 2,800 bucks."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 159284.0,
      "end_time": 161417.0,
      "text": "There isn't really saving much in terms of"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 161417.0,
      "end_time": 163807.0,
      "text": "the agony of dealing with\na car dealership here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 163807.0,
      "end_time": 165897.0,
      "text": "but you are gonna be saving a ton of money"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 165897.0,
      "end_time": 168756.0,
      "text": "over the cost over those five years."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 168756.0,
      "end_time": 171657.0,
      "text": "But what if we look at the\nactual details year by year?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 171657.0,
      "end_time": 173983.0,
      "text": "So on the left here I have each car"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 173983.0,
      "end_time": 176905.0,
      "text": "and then year by year I have\nthe actual cost of maintenance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 176905.0,
      "end_time": 179508.0,
      "text": "and you can see that as time goes on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 179508.0,
      "end_time": 181620.0,
