    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 181620.0,
      "end_time": 183726.0,
      "text": "the costs just tend to go up and up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 183726.0,
      "end_time": 187231.0,
      "text": "where as the Audi and the\nTesla are all pretty flat."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 187231.0,
      "end_time": 189833.0,
      "text": "In fact Audi actually looks\nlike it decreases over time"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 189833.0,
      "end_time": 191412.0,
      "text": "which is kind of nice."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 191412.0,
      "end_time": 192820.0,
      "text": "So I guess when you think about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 192820.0,
      "end_time": 194569.0,
      "text": "there aren't gonna be\nany big surprises here"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 194569.0,
      "end_time": 196959.0,
      "text": "with the Tesla or the\nAudi for that matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 196959.0,
      "end_time": 199391.0,
      "text": "Now if we wanna compare\non a percentage basis"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 199391.0,
      "end_time": 201929.0,
      "text": "and we wanna look at let's\ntake the most expensive Tesla"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 201929.0,
