    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 211075.0,
      "end_time": 214552.0,
      "text": "you're actually still\nsaving about 241 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 214552.0,
      "end_time": 218520.0,
      "text": "close to 7,000 dollars\nover the cheapest car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 218520.0,
      "end_time": 220440.0,
      "text": "the similar gas powered car."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 220440.0,
      "end_time": 223939.0,
      "text": "Compare that to the BMW and\nyou're at 500 percent savings"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223939.0,
      "end_time": 225923.0,
      "text": "and the Mercedes-Benz S-Class you're near"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 225923.0,
      "end_time": 229293.0,
      "text": "550 percent savings, almost 15,000 dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 229293.0,
      "end_time": 231811.0,
      "text": "or North of 15,000\ndollars that you're saving"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 231811.0,
      "end_time": 233923.0,
      "text": "in maintenance costs alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 233923.0,
      "end_time": 235928.0,
      "text": "That's a big deal and that really adds up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 235928.0,
      "end_time": 238467.0,
      "text": "and this is only a five year comparison."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 238467.0,
      "end_time": 240899.0,
      "text": "Now I know a lot of you\nare out there thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 240899.0,
      "end_time": 242627.0,
      "text": "well what about the\nreplacement of the battery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 242627.0,
      "end_time": 244419.0,
      "text": "I've even had people comment saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 244419.0,
      "end_time": 245997.0,
      "text": "you know you have to replace\nthe battery every year"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 245997.0,
      "end_time": 247960.0,
      "text": "which I'm yet to find data on."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 247960.0,
      "end_time": 250947.0,
      "text": "But the way it works is there\nis a eight year warranty"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 250947.0,
      "end_time": 254893.0,
      "text": "on your Tesla battery, and\nit's an infinite mile warranty"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 254893.0,
      "end_time": 257539.0,
      "text": "up to eight years, so any\nproblems you have before that"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 257539.0,
      "end_time": 259437.0,
      "text": "they're gonna replace it for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 259437.0,
      "end_time": 261827.0,
      "text": "But after that the cost\nthat we're looking at"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 261827.0,
      "end_time": 264131.0,
      "text": "is about 12,000 dollars to replace it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 264131.0,
      "end_time": 266072.0,
      "text": "that's based on current standards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 266072.0,
      "end_time": 268163.0,
      "text": "exactly how they're producing them now."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 268163.0,
      "end_time": 271640.0,
      "text": "So if we were to forecast\nout let's say eight years"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 271640.0,
      "end_time": 273389.0,
      "text": "from when you bought your Tesla"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 273389.0,
      "end_time": 274989.0,
      "text": "so that we're eight years from now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 274989.0,
      "end_time": 276547.0,
      "text": "the price of producing the batteries"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 276547.0,
      "end_time": 277976.0,
      "text": "is gonna continue to drop."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 277976.0,
      "end_time": 280280.0,
      "text": "So if we were to take\nthe 12,000 dollars now"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 280280.0,
      "end_time": 282968.0,
      "text": "and reduce it down to say 8,000 dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 282968.0,
      "end_time": 286989.0,
      "text": "and then add that in to the\ncost here of our maintenance"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 286989.0,
      "end_time": 289591.0,
      "text": "and let's just assume that we absorbed"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 289591.0,
      "end_time": 292407.0,
      "text": "all of those 8,000 dollars\nwithin the first five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 292407.0,
      "end_time": 294281.0,
      "text": "again it's a little wonky but I'm trying"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 294281.0,
      "end_time": 296303.0,
      "text": "to appease anybody that has concerns"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 296303.0,
      "end_time": 298479.0,
      "text": "about replacing the batteries here."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 298479.0,
      "end_time": 301380.0,
      "text": "If you wanted to do that\nyou would be a little bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 301380.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "over on the Audi, you'd be\nsaving a little bit on money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 308121.0,
      "text": "the 1.3 thousand or 12\npercent over the Audi A7,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 308121.0,
      "end_time": 311193.0,
      "text": "but then you're still\nsaving close to 60 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 311193.0,
      "end_time": 313753.0,
      "text": "on the BMW and nearly 70 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 313753.0,
      "end_time": 316313.0,
      "text": "over the Mercedes-Benz S-Class."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 316313.0,
      "end_time": 319434.0,
      "text": "So you're still saving\nsix to 7,000 dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 319434.0,
      "end_time": 321043.0,
      "text": "compared to these other cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 321043.0,
      "end_time": 323335.0,
      "text": "that's with the assumption\nthat you would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 323335.0,
      "end_time": 326897.0,
      "text": "replacing the battery on\nyour own within five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 326897.0,
      "end_time": 329244.0,
      "text": "which really isn't gonna happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 329244.0,
      "end_time": 331335.0,
      "text": "Now I'll put a caveat out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
